&yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligine we&nbsp;<b>horlanmaga seb&auml;p&nbsp;</b>bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328;
diagnozy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sorag
we g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmanlar
&uuml;&ccedil;in alamatlary&#328; tebigaty we dowamlylygy, n&auml;sagy&#328;
durmu&#351;ynda pankreatit &uuml;&ccedil;in t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik
faktorlaryny&#328; barlygy barada &ouml;wrenmek m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.&nbsp;Adaty
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmekden we garny&#328; palpasi&yacute;asyndan
ba&#351;ga-da, lukman &yacute;okumly maddalary&#328; &yacute;oklugyna,
horlanmagy&#328;, ganazlygy&#328; alamatlaryna, derini&#328; trofiki
&uuml;&yacute;tgemelerine &uuml;ns berer.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a
barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Biohimiki gan barlagy , &yacute;ok edilende gana
gir&yacute;&auml;n a&#351;gazan asty fermentlerini&#328; (&nbsp;<b>amilaza,
lipaza )&nbsp;</b>&yacute;okary derejesini &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykaryp
biler .&nbsp;Dowamly pankreatitde bu &yacute;iti keselden has az du&#351;
gel&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, dokumalary&#328; &yacute;okumly maddalar
bilen &uuml;pj&uuml;n&ccedil;iligine baha bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in gandaky&nbsp;<b>beloklary&#328;&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>albumini&#328;
umumy mukdary&nbsp;</b>kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zine uly zeper &yacute;etip
bil&yacute;&auml;n s&uuml;&yacute;ji keselini&#328; diagnozy,&nbsp;<b>gliklenen
gemoglobini&#328; derejesini kesgitlemegi talap eder&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Fatagda ere&yacute;&auml;n witaminleri&#328; (A, D, E we K) we B
witaminlerini&#328;&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>derejesi &uuml;&ccedil;in
der&#328;ew&nbsp;, keseli&#328; uzak m&ouml;hletli (5 &yacute;yldan gowrak)
dowam etmegi &uuml;&ccedil;in bellenil&yacute;&auml;r, seb&auml;bi olary&#328;
gana si&#328;megi bozul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Zapany &ouml;wrenmek (&nbsp;<b>koprogramma&nbsp;</b>) i&yacute;mit
si&#328;diri&#351; derejesine baha berm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&#351;gazan asty m&auml;z fermentlerini&#328;
&yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligini tassyklamagy&#328; ba&#351;ga bir usuly,&nbsp;<b>nejisd&auml;ki
elastaza-1 derejesini&#328; peselmegi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn&nbsp;<b>bo&#351;lugyny&#328;&nbsp;ultrases&nbsp;</b>barlagy
(&nbsp;a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; k&auml;bir
&uuml;&yacute;tgemelerine, t&ouml;weregind&auml;ki organlary&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yna, a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; da&#351; bilen
petiklenmegine baha berm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa, k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
ultrases barlagynda &yacute;azylan a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328;
&yacute;a&yacute;ramagyny&#328; alamatlary a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini
anyklamak &uuml;&ccedil;in esas d&auml;l.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Endoskopik ultrases&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>adaty
ultrases barlagyndan has k&ouml;p maglumat ber&yacute;&auml;r, esasanam
keseli&#328; ba&#351;langy&ccedil;
d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa, bu amaly&#328;
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy, ulanyly&#351;yny gaty
&ccedil;&auml;klendir&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Hasaplanan tomografi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>we
esasanam&nbsp;<b>damar kontrastly KT&nbsp;</b>a&#351;gazan asty
m&auml;zini&#328; gurlu&#351;y we atrofi&yacute;a derejesi barada has takyk
maglumat ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Magnit-rezonans tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>we&nbsp;<b>magnit-rezonans kolangiopankreatografi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>(MRCP)
hem &ouml;r&auml;n t&auml;sirli.&nbsp;Emma bu g&ouml;zlegler, a&#351;gazan asty
m&auml;zini&#328; suwuny&#328; b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;ykmagyny
&yacute;&ouml;rite bir madda - sekretini&#328; girizilmegi bilen stimulirlemegi
talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu usuly&#328; ulanylmagyny
&ccedil;&auml;klendir&yacute;&auml;n Russi&yacute;ada bu derman
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;Sekresi&yacute;any gyjyndyrmazdan MRI hasaplanan
tomografi&yacute;a bilen de&#328;e&#351;dirilende artykma&ccedil;lygy
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Endoskopiki retrograd holangiopankreatografi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>a&#351;gazan asty kanallaryny&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgemelerini
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu i&#328; gymmatly
anykla&yacute;y&#351; usullaryndan biridir, &yacute;&ouml;ne
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy&#328; &yacute;okary bolmagy seb&auml;pli, di&#328;e
be&yacute;leki g&ouml;zlegler ba&#351;a barmadyk &yacute;agda&yacute;larda
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi
maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Alamatlary &yacute;ok
etmek we kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgemegi&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>- alkogoldan we &ccedil;ilimden doly dynmak.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&yacute;mitlenme&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Dowamly
pankreatiti&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmegi bilen i&yacute;mitden
&yacute;&uuml;z &ouml;w&uuml;rmek, simptomlar &yacute;e&#328;ilenden so&#328;
derrew dietany gi&#328;eltmek has gowudyr.&nbsp;Galan wagtlarda,
fraksi&yacute;a naharlary maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r - g&uuml;nde 5-6 gezek
ownuk b&ouml;leklerde.&nbsp;Alamatlary agyrla&#351;dyrmasa, &yacute;okary belok
we uglewodly di&yacute;eta islen&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;I&yacute;mit
si&#328;diri&#351; fermentlerini&#328; &yacute;eterlik bolmazlygy,
i&yacute;mitlenmegi &ccedil;&auml;klendirmek &uuml;&ccedil;in seb&auml;p
bolmaly d&auml;ldir.&nbsp;I&#328; gowusy, d&uuml;z&uuml;mi we mukdary sagdyn
adamy&#328; i&yacute;mitinden tapawutlanmaly d&auml;ldir.&nbsp;Ferment
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary bilen ferment &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligini
&yacute;ok etmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn agyrysyny a&yacute;yrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>parasetamol&nbsp;</b>&yacute;a-da
steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y be&yacute;leki
dermanlar&nbsp;&yacute;aly&nbsp;<b>analjezikler ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</b>Impacteterlik
d&auml;l t&auml;siri bilen&nbsp;<b>tramadol ulanylyp bilner&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de
bolsa, &#351;e&yacute;le bejergini bellemezden ozal hirurgiki bejergini talap
ed&yacute;&auml;n agyryny&#328; seb&auml;plerini (mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in,
kanallary&#328; da&#351; bilen petiklenmegi) aradan
a&yacute;yrmalydyr.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>K&auml;bir hadysalarda pregabalin seri&#351;desi&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>agyry kesiji seri&#351;deleri&#328; t&auml;sirini
&yacute;okarlandyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanylyp bilner&nbsp;, bu bolsa
birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n depressi&yacute;any&#328; &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykmagyny azald&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Agyrylandyryjy seri&#351;deleri kabul edeni&#328;den
&uuml;&ccedil; a&yacute;y&#328; i&ccedil;inde agyry gowula&#351;masa,
endoskopiki &yacute;a-da hirurgiki gaty&#351;ma g&ouml;z &ouml;&#328;&uuml;nde
tutulmalydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Fermentleri &yacute;eterlik bolmasa, ferment preparatlaryny
(&nbsp;<b>pankreatin&nbsp;</b>) ulan&yacute;arlar.&nbsp;I&#328; t&auml;sirli
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklar mikrotablet &yacute;a-da ki&ccedil;i mikrosfera
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde bol&yacute;ar, seb&auml;bi a&#351;gazany&#328;
kislotaly gur&#351;awynda bozulma&yacute;ar we i&yacute;mit bilen i&ccedil;ege
gir&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&#351;gazan gidroklor tur&#351;usyny&#328; t&auml;sirini azaltmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in antisekretory dermanlar, esasanam&nbsp;<b>rabeprazol ulanylyp
bilner&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>S&uuml;&yacute;ji keselini&#328; &ouml;smegi bilen
uglewodlary&#328; kabul edilmegini &ccedil;&auml;klendir&yacute;&auml;n berhiz
maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r we &yacute;eterlik derejede t&auml;sirli
bolmasa,&nbsp;<b>insulini ta&yacute;&yacute;arlamagy birikdirmeli&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derman bejergisini&#328; fonunda simptomlary&#328; doly &yacute;ok
edilmegi bilen,&nbsp;<b>fizioterapi&yacute;a bejergisini ulanmak
bol&yacute;ar&nbsp;</b>: elektroforez, ultrases barlagyna,
magnitoterapi&yacute;a.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
